{
  "stem": "3022.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 105,
      "text": "To us, it was something that we couldn't comprehend.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 106,
      "text": "I mean, these were fellow inmates.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 107,
      "text": "But because we were Jewish and they were Polish, so they staged a pogrom.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 108,
      "text": "And if it wasn't for the SS that came with bayonets on their carbines and the machine guns, probably many people would have gotten killed.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 109,
      "text": "That particular camp, the people in the camp worked in quarries.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 110,
      "text": "They were mining over there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 111,
      "text": "Later, we found out that there was uranium in those mountains and it was for the heavy water or whatever they needed it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 112,
      "text": "So we worked in the quarries in the underground.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 113,
      "text": "In that camp, I came down with my first attack of malaria.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 114,
      "text": "And I was put into a dispensary.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 115,
      "text": "But I stayed in the dispensary during the night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 116,
      "text": "And during the day, my friends used to help me out and help me to walk to the work detail.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 117,
      "text": "Because there was a German officer who was supposedly a medical student and used to come during the day and used to experiment with the people in the sick bay, inject air or liquid and then kill them that way.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 118,
      "text": "The conditions were very, very bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 119,
      "text": "Once a week, we were able to take a 20-second cold shower.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 120,
      "text": "The food that we were given could hardly sustain us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 121,
      "text": "We were slowly losing strength.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 122,
      "text": "My very close friend Milek Salpeter from Tarnow lost three of his toes when the lorry went over his foot.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 123,
      "text": "And he was put in a dispensary.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 124,
      "text": "And on the day we were told that we're being moved from Leitmeritz, I said goodbye to him, because I didn't expect to ever see him again.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 125,
      "text": "And I gave him my soup ration.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 126,
      "text": "Fortunately, he survived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 127,
      "text": "He's in Australia today.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 128,
      "text": "And we were moved to Dachau.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
